{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act20side", "eventName": "理想城：長夏狂歡季", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IC-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "沉浸式遊覽", "storyInfo": "杜林人們正在歡慶著因為穹頂損壞而格外漫長的夏日，而斯第奇告訴請求他修復穹頂的氣候代表，這些地上人就是他找來的幫手。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g1_durinstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$relax_intro", "key": "$relax_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別害羞，特米米，很適合你嘛。", "name": "依娜姆"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "fadetime": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真......真的嗎？", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 450.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，這件泳衣我一眼就看中了，是我喜歡的風格！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這家店的裁縫可真了不起，居然這麼快就能改出適合你身材的款式。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我的身材有什麼問題嗎？最近我有加大訓練運動量的！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#8$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，很可愛。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，那就好，我可不想再被笑話尾巴又粗了......依娜姆不去挑挑看泳衣嗎？", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#7$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就算了。我倒是對剛才那個幫裁縫打下手的金屬腦袋更感興趣。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_robotwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_576_1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "power": 5.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.51, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 600.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杜林的技術嗎......", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是太高超了！", "name": "極境"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從沒喝過如此醇美的酒！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，兄弟，祝你健康！", "name": "微醺的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_573_1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_573_1$1", "name2": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祝我們健康，乾杯！老卡爾蜜釀萬歲！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂特米米，這個叫極境的......真的靠得住嗎？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "特米米", "content": "呃，極境先生關鍵時候還是很厲害的，"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "特米米", "end": "true", "content": "大概！", "joined": "呃，極境先生關鍵時候還是很厲害的，大概！"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，羅德島上也有杜林族幹員，但他們從來不說自己城市的事情呢。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#7$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道杜林族有什麼隱藏的秘密？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我覺得他們只是不太在意，他們大概更關心中午食堂吃什麼。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真沒想到，我們居然有機會來到建在地下的杜林城市。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，這或許是讓嘉維爾的名字在杜林人裡也傳播開的大好機會......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這次休假，居然沒拉著嘉維爾、祖瑪瑪和克瑪爾一起回來嗎？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克瑪爾說她想和煌小姐一起練拳。嘉維爾和祖瑪瑪去出任務了還沒回來。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "特米米", "content": "嘉維爾最近實在是太累了，讓人操心！"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "特米米", "end": "true", "content": "真希望她能不要這麼勉強自己......", "joined": "嘉維爾最近實在是太累了，讓人操心！真希望她能不要這麼勉強自己......"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我走之前給她們留了信，把你們發現斯第奇先生的事，還有斯第奇先生說的話都寫下來了。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是她們能借著這個機會回阿卡胡拉休息一下就好了......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那兩個傢伙，還有你，當初二話不說就讓我當了這裡的大酋長，也該回來看看我勉為其難了這麼久的成果吧。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說句題外話，你們平時在羅德島的時候有沒有覺得，這個叫極境的，有點煩人？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔哦哦，完全不同的風味！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高個子，我看你剛才和那幫喜歡蜜釀的傢伙混在一起，聽我一句，那就是兒童飲料！", "name": "大醉的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真正的好東西還得看咱們七號烈酒，來，乾杯。", "name": "大醉的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "乾杯！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這香氣，是暴雨過後的雨林，地下溶洞中苔蘚的味道......!", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_574_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊抱歉，是木頭杯子有點發霉了。", "name": "大醉的杜林人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_574_1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來他倒的確樂在其中。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，依娜姆，你還沒和我說過，在哪遇到斯第奇先生的呢。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......這就說來話長了。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_jungle_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.6, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 大酋長，你上次帶來的大傢伙可真帶勁！對著那些東西，我已經通了好幾個宵啦！", "name": "興奮的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這幾天我老婆天天唸我，說我的魂都快被這些東西勾走了！", "name": "興奮的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不就是幾台哥倫比亞的報廢車床嗎，不至於吧。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那可太至於了！傳說中的製造機器的機器！你體會過那東西在你面前運轉起來的感覺嗎？我和我老婆戀愛的時候，心都沒跳得這麼快過！", "name": "興奮的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唔，改天我讓人給你的車床裝個減震。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 特米米再過些日子要回來了，得早做準備，去接她一下。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 接特米米？我已經能想像出那得是多繁重的體力勞動了。", "name": "不再興奮的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "約等於被車床揍了一頓的勞累吧。", "name": "唉聲歎氣的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 天知道她又會帶多少收藏品回來！上次她寄回來的包裹，我們去了幾個人搬？", "name": "不再興奮的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我一開始還以為那是一整支商隊！", "name": "不再興奮的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特米米她從小就是這樣沒錯啦，總喜歡收集一些亂七八糟的東西......", "name": "唉聲歎氣的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，她去羅德島的這幾年，是不是有點變本加厲了？", "name": "唉聲歎氣的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我是搞不懂為什麼她要把嘉維爾打穿的鋼板寄回來。", "name": "不再興奮的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_071"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_071", "name2": "avg_npc_070", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說是因為在羅德島的宿舍放不下了。", "name": "唉聲歎氣的阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 等等，前面是不是有人？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_jungleentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一定是瘋了才上來找罪受。先是那一串七拐八繞的洞窟，然後又是這麼一片鬼地方！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可地心那老傢伙也實在是太煩了，每天就是堵著門嘮嘮叨叨......嘖，這些討厭的藤蔓！這該死的太陽！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然人造光源要比這玩意好得多！", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好渴，睏了。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完全無法理解老師為什麼要離開際崖城，找不痛快嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 小孩子？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你才是小孩子！", "name": "小孩子？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 唔，好奇怪的口音，誰教你的？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我自學的，不滿意？", "name": "小孩子？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 小孩子要有禮貌，和別人說話不許這麼不耐煩。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這人長得好奇怪，阿卡胡拉還有這樣的人？是誰家走失的孩子嗎？", "name": "阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不是粗尾巴，也不是細尾巴......", "name": "阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 也不是黎博利或者斐迪亞，不，等等，難道你是......", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你是杜林人吧？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 杜林？杜林人是什麼人？", "name": "阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我也只在雜誌上看到過，據說是一種生活在地下的奇怪種族。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 那不是磐蟹嗎？", "name": "阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你才是磐蟹呢！找揍嗎！", "name": "也許是磐蟹？"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 哦！我想起來了！前幾年的《奇談怪論》上寫過，據說杜林人的釀酒水準很高，這一點和磐蟹不太一樣。", "name": "阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 磐蟹最多也就吃點發酵的水果把自己搞醉。", "name": "阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 而且磐蟹也不是生活在地下，它們只是會用土把自己埋起來而已。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重點不是在那裡吧！", "name": "不是磐蟹"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，果然，地上人就是一群目光短淺的自大狂，什麼都不懂還喜歡到處發表議論。", "name": "不是磐蟹"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡直比杜林人還蠢。", "name": "不是磐蟹"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，最重要的是，審美也糟得很。", "name": "不是磐蟹"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 喂，小杜林，我穿的可是薩爾貢最流行的款式。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "選擇所謂的“流行款式”就足夠證明你審美的糟糕程度了。被別人塑造的審美有什麼價值？可悲的附庸罷了。", "name": "小杜林"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 大酋長，這小子是不是有點欠修理？", "name": "阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 畢竟年紀還小，算了算了。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早就成年了！", "name": "小杜林"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#3$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我和這些傻子囉嗦什麼，告辭。", "name": "成年的小杜林"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 啊，那個小孩子走掉了欸。", "name": "阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_070"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 嗯？又停住了？", "name": "阿達克利斯人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_070"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說......", "name": "成年的小杜林"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......咳，我說，如果不太介意的話，地上人......", "name": "成年的小杜林"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能給口水喝嗎？", "name": "成年的小杜林"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g1_durinstreet", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，後來就是你在發給我的信裡寫的那樣，他說杜林人的城市遇到了一點小麻煩，需要我們的幫忙？", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "起碼當時這位斯第奇是這麼聲稱的。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "content": "看看我們的周圍！這漂亮的城市，哪有......"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "end": "true", "content": "嗝！哪有一點有麻煩的樣子？", "joined": "看看我們的周圍！這漂亮的城市，哪有......嗝！哪有一點有麻煩的樣子？"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，酒太好喝或許也是麻煩，容易把人喝趴下，不過我倒是沒醉，乾杯！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個彆扭的小鬼大概只是想邀請我們參觀一下他那些漂亮的房子吧，完全可以理解。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別把誰都想得和你一樣，極境。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇在我們這裡住了一個月，有一天看見了那些正在折騰造火車的阿達克利斯人。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後他說，呃，“夠專業！你們焊的這些破銅爛鐵能幫上我的大忙！要不要來際崖城看看？”", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "content": "你就——兄弟，麻煩添滿，剩下的這點我先乾了——"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#6"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "end": "true", "content": "你就這麼答應了？", "joined": "你就——兄弟，麻煩添滿，剩下的這點我先乾了——你就這麼答應了？"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然斯第奇極力渲染了一場危機......其實我主要還是為了滿足一下自己的好奇心，順便看看和我們地下的鄰居有沒有生意可做。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好功利！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿卡胡拉要想擺脫野蠻的狀態，現在可是什麼都缺啊。聽說杜林族的冶煉和製造技術都很厲害，要是能幫他們這個忙，換上一兩樣......", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們也不用再為搞到了點報廢品就興奮半天了。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依娜姆......你居然真的在好好當大酋長啊！我還以為你會天天去城裡買東西，然後把錢都花光。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這孩子，平日裡就是這麼看我的？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿卡胡拉想要發展，最重要的當然是錢，薩爾貢金幣也好，哥倫比亞金券也好，維多利亞鎊也好，我們全都需要。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是就憑藉現在阿卡胡拉的產出——一些粗陋的手工製品，一些未精煉的礦石，別說賺錢了，連讓大家過上好日子都勉勉強強。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，好在你們也不在乎城市裡定義的那種“好日子”。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，錢和財富是有區別的，一味地累積錢財什麼都帶不來，真正流動起來的才能被稱作“財富”。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿卡胡拉正在變好，而要變得更好，還需要一個契機。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如說，和杜林人的技術合作。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，開始聽不懂了......反正對我來說，遇到困難就用法術！法術不行就用法杖敲！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#5$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是我們“嘉維爾意志”的生活方式！", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈，你怎麼在羅德島待了這麼久，還是這一套？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，唉，我能做到的也就是這些細枝末節的事情了，想讓阿卡胡拉發展起來，還需要一個，“領袖”。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，依娜姆你不就是大酋長嗎？", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領袖是能把你們提亞卡烏真正團結在一起的傢伙。我？我可嫌麻煩。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我寧願去城裡逛街。", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#2"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好的設想！我也喜歡逛街，不過更喜歡野外，嗝！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#2"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，是不是有個吵吵鬧鬧的小個子消失好久了？藏到哪裡去玩了嗎？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像是哎......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概是去做準備了吧？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，不過，既然大滑梯就在眼前......先放鬆一下也沒什麼問題吧？", "name": "依娜姆"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_075"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我聽羅德島上的炎國幹員說過一個詞！叫......叫什麼“客隨主便”......來著？", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概的意思就是，既然主人不在，客人就可以隨便了。", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#4$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗝！說得好！為了這句話我得再喝一杯！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#3"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_401_elysm_na_1#5"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朋友們，我們來比比誰先到大滑梯腳下！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "char_401_elysm_na_1#5"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_075", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......極境先生，適應杜林人生活的速度，還真是快呢......", "name": "特米米"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_572_1#2$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "30_g10_lakegarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，呼，終於擺脫那幫醉鬼了。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#10$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以說我討厭這些沒心沒肺的杜林人！這些傢伙都把寶貴的生命浪費在了什麼上面！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "才走了一個月，際崖城真是又醜了不少。唉！我就不該回來！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#6$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那幾個傻乎乎的地上人呢？嘖，只要他們能修出不至於塌掉的鐵路橋，我的標準也不是不能放低一點......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇？你真的回來了！我聽說有個不會喝酒的杜林在際崖城裡亂跑，就猜到是你！", "name": "杜林老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶奇·地心......你還真是陰魂不散。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這段時間到底跑到哪裡去了？我到處找你，就快拼著老命去塌方的山洞那裡看看了！", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#8$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這條老命可硬得很，倒是我，差點就死了。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道......你去了地上？！", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，不可以嗎？", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇，我真是沒想到。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你好大的膽子，你居然......", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#4$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "居然這麼有出息！快，讓我看看你帶回來了什麼稀奇玩意！", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1"}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "升降梯上面那串山洞太難走了，地圖又不知道放去哪裡了，好些年沒人願意上去玩了！", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總給我帶了點禮物吧！遠方的礦石標本？地上特有的釀酒植物？難道是最新的《奇談怪論》？！圖書館裡的那一批都過期好久了。", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，呃，怎麼說呢......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#5$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我帶了幾個人回來。", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}, "figure_art": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_4054_malist_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "耶奇·地心"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_564_1#5$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_caveentrance", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“於是，她選擇了......”", "name": "思考的魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“她選擇了老卡爾蜜釀！”", "name": "思考的魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，不太好，是不是產品進入得太慢了？得稍微改一下......", "name": "思考的魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#9$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“比划算更划算，比瘋狂還瘋狂！”", "name": "思考的魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“如果你想找到一片讓人盡情享受的土地，一段可以肆意玩樂的時間，當然，還有一口安撫靈魂的蜜酒——”", "name": "思考的魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“認准際崖城的老卡爾蜜釀！”", "name": "思考的魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#5$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，簡潔明快，直白大方，委託人應該會喜歡的，但願。", "name": "思考的魯珀"}, "figure_art": "avg_4055_bgsnow_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}